window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Deadwood carpenter, Isaiah Yates, knows that he’ll never marry because of the secret he holds close, but he wishes things were different, especially after he meets the beautiful young widow, Leanne Moss. Leanne feels something spark between her and Isaiah, but why is the man avoiding her? Isaiah seems to be a man of integrity who would make a wonderful husband and father for her five children. However, since every other man has run when they learned of her large family, she decides to keep the children a secret until Isaiah gets to know her – if he’ll ever stay in her company long enough to get to know her.</p>"; 
